Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸陸續續的凋零、隕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有超過壹仟億以上的恒星被消滅掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從三百八十萬光年的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸的，從永劫的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步一步的往地球逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個水藍色的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後也會被黑暗的餘幕所攏罩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會有一位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有這一場浩劫關鍵之鑰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位少女是一位擁有預知能力的超能力感應者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底的空白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在於這個大宇宙中的所有一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必須徹底的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:06:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托蘭西爾巴尼亞國的第一公主  露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將以親善大使的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛往美國做巡迴訪問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會發生這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架噴機會墜機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜公主，請您先冷靜下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是已經死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼可能會死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你是超世紀的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是以意識體的形態存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是距離銀河系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約三百八十萬光年的宇宙空間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做扶洛依
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶洛依
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算找也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有以固有的形態出現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在特定的場所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在是直接用意識在溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換彼此的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心電感應？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要做任何防衛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡管放心 敞開妳的意識就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺好像充滿了 無邊無際的穩定力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越知覺的能力也就是超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為信賴而覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為愛才得到了這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是宇宙意識中的能量生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶洛依 為什麼帶我到這個地方來？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有東西想給妳看傳送影像給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球徹底消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅只有十億年的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數的星雲，無數的大宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經消失怠盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兇爆的能量生命體幻魔所幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個為了破壞而不停破壞的純粹破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向幻魔挑戰的戰亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從無限的過去持續到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個宇宙中最勇敢的激動戰士貝葛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的戰鬥持續了二百年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當他的愛人雅利愛達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因幻魔而斷送生命時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失意的戰士貝葛就變成了殘兵敗卒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是二千年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幻魔大王的魔掌已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擴展到妳所屬的銀河系宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在致命的膠囊裡面持續了二千年的沈睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因此得以保住性命的戰士 貝葛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為幻魔的策略被放逐到銀河系的盡頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了抹殺掉不久之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就會知道幻魔存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位住在地球上的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯，就是為了殺妳 露娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，在這個瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托來西爾巴尼亞國的第一公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜公主的生涯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經就此畫下句點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就表示全新的超能力戰士 露娜的誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一個很平凡的女孩子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我要為了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是為了什麼要戰鬥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了妳自己本身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你們地球人都充滿了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友愛與友情的連帶關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有追求至高無尚的價值的一顆熱情的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以正面能量的形態結合在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球應該就可以擁有打敗幻魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所擁有的負面能量的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從漫長沉睡中甦醒的時刻來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經失去了同胞 朋友和所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想維持原狀繼續沈睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回想看看啊，貝葛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經，對身為生化戰士的你表白愛意的一位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做雅利愛達的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以會從二千年的沈睡中甦醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你身為戰士的知覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她對你的愛情告白的實證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是扶洛依的意指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶洛依
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道扶洛依的存在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是地球的超能力戰士 露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說，我就是在等這一天 這一刻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 沒問題的，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油 沖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點，快點 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 就快到了，就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺不賴的嘛 錄選正式球員了耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯喔！不錯喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！主將，以後全都靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說藏決定退出社團了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個打擊也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要退出棒球社團
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經被選為正式球員了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法二者兼顧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇專心的準備考試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右外野手的位置 我想就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我沒有同情你的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大西洋上空失蹤的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托蘭四世記航空336班機的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據事發後的調查結果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能沒有人員生還
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這起事故而痛失第一公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜公主的托蘭西爾巴尼亞國的國民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都陷入了極端的哀傷中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外，有關當局對失事原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍在繼續的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，你回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然約我出來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我問妳怎麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳最近都不肯跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，妳每次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會我們要去那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好了，我帶你去一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還沒有回答我喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得，你這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像沒事找我吵架一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺很難受耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前根本就沒有發生過這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們兩個 最好暫時先不要見面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我心裡是喜歡藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就是受不了他那個姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個不錯的地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.33,0:24:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去玩啊\N走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.44,0:24:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是個高中生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，未滿十八歲是不能購票進場的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.12,0:24:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你走路不長眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.79,0:24:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.40,0:25:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.88,0:26:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊，救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.21,0:26:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊，請你救救我 警察先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.32,0:26:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.62,0:27:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能，怎麼都死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.19,0:27:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都變的跟石頭一樣堅硬
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.19,0:27:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜止不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.30,0:28:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要把我怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.62,0:29:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這可惡的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.30,0:30:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.35,0:30:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.48,0:30:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.16,0:30:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.54,0:31:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，藏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.98,0:31:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.84,0:31:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.67,0:31:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經搞清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.27,0:32:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一場夢，全都是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.07,0:32:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這莫名其妙的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.81,0:32:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做夢，真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.85,0:32:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.65,0:32:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.08,0:32:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能運用那麼驚人瞬間爆發的念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.39,0:32:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們預計的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.39,0:32:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超乎想像了 如果慢一步發射防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.23,0:32:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.10,0:32:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的很多做法實在是太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.14,0:32:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.34,0:32:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有些超能力戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.34,0:32:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不把他們逼至恐怖的極限狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.08,0:32:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有辦法覺醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.38,0:32:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的危險現在才要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.02,0:32:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.58,0:32:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的解放真正含意是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.70,0:33:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我看慣了的臉孔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.70,0:33:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看慣了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.30,0:33:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看慣了的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.97,0:33:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.44,0:33:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是平常過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.62,0:33:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.97,0:33:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不是在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.54,0:33:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我以前看慣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.77,0:33:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上好像發生了不尋常的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.84,0:35:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都飛起來了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.54,0:35:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.32,0:35:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運用精神的力量移動或搬動物體
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.82,0:35:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是念動力也是超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.96,0:35:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然擁有這種力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.93,0:36:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你的精神怎麼這麼好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.80,0:37:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常就這樣了啊 沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.17,0:37:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.20,0:37:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有點擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.81,0:37:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事那麼高興啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.51,0:37:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.24,0:37:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四郎，我問你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.18,0:37:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相不相信超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.91,0:37:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.88,0:37:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會相信那種曖昧不明的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.52,0:37:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是真的存在耶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.36,0:37:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.96,0:37:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠讓我親眼看到的話那就另當別論
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.19,0:37:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到就會相信了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.60,0:37:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下來，放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.20,0:37:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，我拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.91,0:37:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快放我下來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.51,0:37:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.41,0:37:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是你幹的好事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.08,0:37:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力是真實存在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.49,0:37:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你到底相不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.39,0:38:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛看到的一切就是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.76,0:38:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的可以運用那種力量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.00,0:38:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子你就相信了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.63,0:38:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用力量隨心所欲操控別人的行為嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.20,0:38:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.20,0:38:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才…我才不會認同那種自我優越主義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.18,0:38:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會承認超能力的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.34,0:38:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會認同的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.78,0:38:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷靜下來嘛，四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.75,0:38:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.18,0:38:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從今天開始就跟你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.54,0:38:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純子跟四郎都離我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.41,0:38:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都離開我的身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.62,0:39:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都會有那種經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.29,0:39:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦力量甦醒後
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮與孤獨就會相繼來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.80,0:39:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也會沒辦法抗拒想知道真相的誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.27,0:39:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道自己的力量大到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.48,0:39:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們也很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.75,0:39:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.92,0:39:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就測驗一下他的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.65,0:39:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.68,0:39:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在正陷入苦惱中沒有那種餘力
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.25,0:39:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.29,0:39:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著用心電感應
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.06,0:39:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們的影像傳送給藏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.30,0:39:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，你還沒睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.24,0:39:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要進去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.48,0:40:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是發燒了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.89,0:40:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.63,0:40:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.93,0:40:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.70,0:40:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊！我是姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.04,0:40:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.56,0:40:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.20,0:40:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點二馬赫 那是跟噴射機一樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.20,0:41:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經設定好而且飛行的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.57,0:41:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.27,0:41:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底要跟到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.74,0:41:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再試一次用心電感應跟他接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.21,0:41:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.21,0:41:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還不知道該如何控制自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.85,0:41:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.62,0:41:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果不突破這個磨練
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.25,0:41:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有辦法掌握那種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.93,0:41:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這次要傳送什麼給他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.10,0:41:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送事實 傳送扶洛依所告訴我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.38,0:41:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.42,0:41:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.89,0:41:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是異區跟大宇宙的破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.26,0:42:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻魔大王戰鬥的超能力戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.20,0:42:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士…幻魔又是什麼玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.21,0:42:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.71,0:42:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.21,0:42:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.85,0:42:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.69,0:42:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在於這個大宇宙裡的所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.22,0:42:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都要毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.46,0:42:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.30,0:42:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.87,0:42:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球最徹底的滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.11,0:42:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.75,0:42:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.95,0:42:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.98,0:42:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.86,0:43:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏\N千萬不要捲入幻魔的影像裡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.13,0:43:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.01,0:43:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所害怕的事好像已經發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.38,0:43:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是衝擊太強烈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.35,0:43:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟由映像所控制的幻魔戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.95,0:43:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且相信自己是幻魔的手下敗將
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.49,0:43:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子好像是精神機能出現了障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.06,0:43:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在心裡立起了一道牆
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.33,0:43:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己封閉在很深奧的黑暗裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.36,0:43:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣下去就是廢人了 怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.76,0:43:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只好利用心電感應
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.13,0:43:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入他的深層意識
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.04,0:43:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他帶回這個現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.04,0:43:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.77,0:43:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心深處的黑暗是超乎想像的迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.08,0:43:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險程度連熟練的催眠治療師
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.75,0:43:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有可能發生意外
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.05,0:44:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.35,0:44:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.55,0:44:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不可以失去藏
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.94,0:44:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.42,0:44:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.22,0:44:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏\N又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.53,0:44:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，等一下\N請妳繞了我好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.44,0:45:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.52,0:45:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.32,0:45:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.79,0:45:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，已經沒有什麼好害怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.92,0:45:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.59,0:45:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖，不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.19,0:45:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看姐姐就在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.20,0:45:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小我就待在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.37,0:45:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後也永遠不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.82,0:45:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說那裡就是你最終的避護所了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.86,0:45:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請問你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.33,0:45:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來是為了找藏
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.86,0:45:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，可以請你先離開嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.33,0:45:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.67,0:46:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏\N你為什麼要一直逃避呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.47,0:46:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你在逃避些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.81,0:46:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在逃避你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.71,0:46:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為你逃的了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.05,0:46:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.35,0:46:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏\N拜託你請你離開那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.72,0:46:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.05,0:46:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.19,0:46:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在所依靠的並不是你現實的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.03,0:46:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從你的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.03,0:46:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所衍生出來自我主義的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.86,0:46:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自我逃避的偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.50,0:46:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是實體只是個虛偽幻象罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.00,0:47:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.40,0:47:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超能力戰士露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.17,0:47:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是敵人還是朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.87,0:47:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切就要看你怎麼想了 藏
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.20,0:47:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了，露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.85,0:48:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好累，好睏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.79,0:48:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.30,0:48:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，貝葛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.90,0:48:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛才已經用心電感應告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.90,0:48:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是因為情報量實在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.90,0:48:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有點混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.74,0:48:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要思考自己應該做什麼就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.08,0:48:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦集中精神運用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.29,0:48:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會覺得非常的疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.72,0:48:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果運用過度可能會變成廢人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.53,0:48:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴重還有可能會喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.63,0:48:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用法錯誤的話
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.33,0:48:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.60,0:48:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至會危及其它眾多的無辜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.80,0:48:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.67,0:48:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在已查覺到自己的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.77,0:48:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到你可以自由控制那股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.61,0:48:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是個戰士了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.18,0:48:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那個時候再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.08,0:48:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.85,0:49:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進入你深層意識之前
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.22,0:49:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾經說過 她絕對不可以失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.22,0:49:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說 每個人都有不可或缺的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.30,0:49:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有查覺到這點的人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.73,0:49:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有資格成為戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.73,0:49:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來了，桑比
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.20,0:49:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始捕捉超能力者了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.03,0:49:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來呀，桑比
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.71,0:50:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在開什麼玩笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.95,0:50:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是幻魔大王的命令好了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.72,0:50:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手也只不過是個女孩跟小鬼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.04,0:50:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些話 等你消失他們之後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.79,0:50:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你負責去追補藏
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.53,0:50:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.47,0:51:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來了，札梅帝
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.00,0:51:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有資格對我下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.48,0:51:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經連續睡三天三夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.25,0:51:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候他為什麼會突然消失呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.36,0:51:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有回來的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.56,0:52:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又為什麼會睡在房間裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.20,0:52:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.97,0:52:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本毫無頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.81,0:52:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.86,0:53:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興你來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.06,0:53:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得突然想見妳一面
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.90,0:53:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.33,0:53:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想為之前的事情跟你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.30,0:53:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.04,0:53:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏\N你這幾天都沒有來學校上課
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.21,0:53:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到你之後
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.08,0:53:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於了解了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.88,0:53:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心裡到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.72,0:53:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你 我不想在繼續逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.79,0:53:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.62,0:53:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你原諒我，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.59,0:53:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事就別再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.23,0:53:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.87,0:53:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.10,0:53:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.44,0:53:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.61,0:53:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家人都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.09,0:54:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟平常不太一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.19,0:54:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，我變了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.56,0:54:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 怎麼會有這種怪味道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.37,0:54:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.30,0:54:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不是純子
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.43,0:54:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡那種味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.66,0:54:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就讓你多聞一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.81,0:55:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量聞，用力的聞
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.01,0:55:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞到死為止
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.44,0:56:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，我要開燈了 不要開燈
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.98,0:56:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.85,0:56:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.89,0:56:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N我說了妳也不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.33,0:56:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.04,0:56:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.81,0:56:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.02,0:56:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嚇到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.36,0:56:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐，妳還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.36,0:57:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的時候妳帶我去遊樂場玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.70,0:57:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.30,0:57:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.94,0:57:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這兩三天
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.24,0:57:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在回想那個時候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.31,0:57:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕喔！沒關係，不會怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.18,0:57:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕喔！別怕，別怕
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.08,0:57:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我還想再去玩一次
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.05,0:57:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以呀，什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.32,0:57:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.84,0:57:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 因為這就是你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.88,0:57:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.51,0:57:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是姐姐 這種天馬行空的事
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.25,0:57:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然就這樣接受了好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.76,0:58:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是你說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.36,0:58:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼事我都會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.73,0:58:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴妳真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.68,0:58:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我好像殺了人了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.96,0:58:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是有可能是我的精神錯亂了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.20,0:58:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光在想就已經很可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.20,0:58:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情很難保持平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.87,0:58:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就是一個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.21,0:58:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就沒有勇氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.88,0:58:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，那些突然的變化讓你困惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.61,0:59:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是思考就已經讓你精疲力竭
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.35,0:59:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.75,0:59:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃避自己的煩惱跟痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.02,0:59:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能勇敢的面對並克服它們
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.23,0:59:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你保護你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.90,0:59:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟保護別人是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.87,0:59:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.00,0:59:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在你想保護別人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.17,0:59:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所湧現出來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.31,0:59:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.58,0:59:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你記住這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.41,0:59:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後你所能依靠的 其實就只有愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.89,0:59:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我好像從好幾輩子以前
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.99,0:59:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經認識你了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.26,0:59:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然來世也是一樣 你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.20,0:59:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐隨時都會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.91,0:59:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，如果我沒有猜錯的話
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.04,1:00:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實純子也是幻魔設下的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.34,1:00:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.31,1:00:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這是很合理的推測
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.08,1:00:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好驚訝喔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.55,1:00:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然可以馬上做那種聯想
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.19,1:00:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是看透了所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.59,1:00:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許\N我這種能力跟你的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.83,1:00:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這也是力量的話
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.46,1:00:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有愛跟勇氣
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.90,1:00:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都可以成為超能力者
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.20,1:00:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的耶
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.27,1:00:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐，讓我們盡情的飛吧！\N來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.89,1:00:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.06,1:00:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.16,1:00:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏你身上所擁有的偉大力量
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.73,1:00:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是為了你自己個人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.50,1:01:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你應該做的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.27,1:01:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是竭盡全力保護這個美麗的地球
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.21,1:01:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐，我也開始這麼認為了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.68,1:01:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.88,1:01:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記今晚發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.68,1:01:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚一定會成為一個美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.75,1:01:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在我的記憶中
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.64,1:02:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底的破壞
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.61,1:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.75,1:02:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.39,1:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁火打劫偷東西實在是太容易
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.06,1:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊，隨便我們拿耶
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.03,1:03:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.70,1:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大皇冠
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.30,1:03:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把它送給甜心
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.77,1:03:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吻她絕對沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.67,1:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.91,1:03:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.32,1:04:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭甜心
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.66,1:04:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要給她真正的珠寶
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.82,1:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就會任你擺佈了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.23,1:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們撒退吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.73,1:04:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的警戒比平常還要嚴
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.20,1:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快點收拾一下\N好，知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.51,1:04:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經放不下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.21,1:04:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也帶走吧 動作快一點啦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.04,1:04:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.68,1:04:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 索尼
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.05,1:04:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了 快逃，索尼
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.38,1:04:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.85,1:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底的掃射
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.38,1:05:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓這一次我一定要親手\N逮到那個可惡的惡魔小鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.57,1:05:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大你快逃吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.88,1:06:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟的上就儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.50,1:06:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.27,1:06:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住，索尼·尼克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.40,1:07:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主，你為什麼會一直猶饞
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.73,1:07:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送心電感應過去給他呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.27,1:07:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.67,1:07:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們好不容易找到的對象
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.97,1:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是個黑人！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.64,1:07:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是因為他是個小混混呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.09,1:07:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把我關在這種地方也沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.70,1:07:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有辦法穿牆而過
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.93,1:07:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個牢籠
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.27,1:07:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被特殊的能量球防護罩
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.23,1:07:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給徹底的包圍起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.80,1:07:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.75,1:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.48,1:07:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你最好停止無謂的掙扎啦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.88,1:07:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.95,1:07:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.42,1:08:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真正的歐來利署長吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.36,1:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰？你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.43,1:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼你發現了是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.06,1:08:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺聰明的嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.83,1:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為署長身體已經被我給竊占
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.37,1:08:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.90,1:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫札梅帝
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.44,1:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想把我怎麼樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.67,1:08:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你當做逮捕超能力者的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.81,1:08:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說些我聽不懂的話
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.18,1:08:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.85,1:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.25,1:08:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掙扎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.19,1:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意是可以吸收周圍波動的能量磁場
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.69,1:08:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越是用力掙扎它就越膨脹
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.86,1:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.70,1:08:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它最喜歡你那種憎恨的能量你自己看
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.64,1:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要囉嗦，快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.54,1:08:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝擊的破壞的聲音快點放我出去
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.57,1:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它最喜歡的養分
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.58,1:08:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.62,1:09:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尖叫吧 快放我出去！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.35,1:09:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掙扎吧！\N救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.63,1:09:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停的尖叫，掙扎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.64,1:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索尼！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.04,1:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.51,1:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.25,1:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜，妳叫露娜
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.95,1:10:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻魔？幻魔怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.73,1:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇人好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.20,1:10:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅光是怎麼回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.34,1:10:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.17,1:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是露娜傳送的心電感應
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.77,1:10:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.71,1:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紐約陷入恐慌 露娜對我發出求救信號
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.88,1:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我，露娜
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.34,1:11:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳能透視那顆球的真面目嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.51,1:11:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.58,1:11:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是氣體又像是生命體
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.38,1:11:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法確定
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.55,1:11:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是索尼被困在裡面是千真萬確的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.19,1:11:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽絲剝繭出來的答案就只有一個
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.99,1:11:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是幻魔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.69,1:12:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是幻魔那幫人幹的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.03,1:12:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在那裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.60,1:12:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻魔一族並沒有固定的形態
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.27,1:12:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可以溶入所有的事物裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.60,1:12:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以附身在人或物體上面
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.27,1:12:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用心電感應向索尼問出個所以然吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.52,1:12:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.59,1:12:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法在380萬光年的彼方做個了結
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.23,1:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定現在做個了結
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.90,1:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有可能會因此而分離
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.88,1:12:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.01,1:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要跟你一起奮戰到底
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.82,1:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.55,1:12:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為妳現在應該跟自己的猶饞作戰才對
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.62,1:13:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索尼
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.59,1:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又是妳！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.49,1:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平安無事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.33,1:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不穿牆而過呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.76,1:13:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面那道屏障不是那麼好對付的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.36,1:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.90,1:13:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.37,1:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下變成警察
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.57,1:13:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下變成火球的叫札梅帝的怪物
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.04,1:13:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,札梅帝如果是生命體
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.54,1:13:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該會有意志才對呀！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.64,1:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮壁的防護罩太強烈
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.31,1:13:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法讀出來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.42,1:14:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛，你要小心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.62,1:14:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要傷到關在裡面的索尼
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.93,1:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是現身了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.20,1:14:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘存的破銅斕鐵
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.70,1:14:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你知道我是誰就錯不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.20,1:14:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是幻魔一族的札梅帝
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.38,1:14:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是在下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.81,1:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛，我看出球體的弱點了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.28,1:15:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了掩護眼狀的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.18,1:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會旋轉移動的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.22,1:15:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他害怕會被抽出一個洞
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.72,1:15:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.23,1:15:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK防護罩
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.57,1:15:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，你過來支援了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.04,1:16:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛，我傳送給你，你接住喔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.21,1:16:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，幹的好
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.98,1:16:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.25,1:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.19,1:16:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.19,1:16:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.36,1:16:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個眼狀的地方就是能量磁場
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.63,1:16:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把磁場破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.33,1:16:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.57,1:17:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛，快射擊天線
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.01,1:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快前進的脫身
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.89,1:17:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜、貝葛，一切都很順利
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.69,1:17:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就用我的超能力 把那傢伙給消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.46,1:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，住手
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.49,1:17:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種行為會危及急公主的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.20,1:17:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈半道，住我一臂之力吧 我是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.54,1:17:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的力量把我跟公主瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.50,1:17:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.47,1:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在跟這種怪物扯上任何關係了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.11,1:17:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索尼
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.89,1:18:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛，該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.92,1:18:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.36,1:18:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.70,1:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不關我的事呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.77,1:18:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對，你心知肚明了小朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.00,1:18:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是瑜珊行者叫瑜瑾
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.81,1:18:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受到心電感應之後就趕過來了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.91,1:18:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你這時候選擇逃避的話
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.61,1:18:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這輩子就會因為失落感而一獗不振
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.75,1:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士如果失去了優越感
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.65,1:18:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於跟死了一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.86,1:18:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.40,1:18:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.81,1:18:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要接住喔，大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.73,1:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就接不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.30,1:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.00,1:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力整個到齊了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.47,1:19:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.04,1:19:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.35,1:19:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間移動開始
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.79,1:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK防護罩固定
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.70,1:19:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東金振動光放射
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.65,1:20:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.05,1:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個傢伙傳送到意志零了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.32,1:20:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示他從這個世界失了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.05,1:20:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.62,1:20:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.50,1:20:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.10,1:21:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，我沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.20,1:21:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不可以掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.61,1:21:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在傳送之前
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.28,1:21:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經跟本體分離留在地球上了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.52,1:21:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.09,1:21:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快浮出他在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.59,1:21:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量減弱了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.89,1:21:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定去跟在日本的夥伴桑比合體
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.53,1:21:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕獲些人質后再卷土從來
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.95,1:21:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！\N是我姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.42,1:23:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東小姐，東小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.73,1:23:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.70,1:23:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道已經發佈緊急避難令了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.64,1:23:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.61,1:23:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上的人啊已經全數疏散避難去了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.98,1:23:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你盡數離開吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.75,1:23:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…你是不是有什麼困難啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.68,1:23:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我在等我弟弟回來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.12,1:23:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.22,1:23:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.49,1:23:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該馬上就回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.86,1:23:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.23,1:23:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.84,1:23:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？\N那麼我就跟你一起等好了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.73,1:24:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是什麼人啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.10,1:24:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼人也不是
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.97,1:24:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.03,1:24:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑比
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.47,1:25:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不過是個女人
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.94,1:25:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還客氣什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.64,1:25:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了，札梅帝 我現在正要動手而已
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.58,1:25:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.20,1:25:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是幻魔的手下
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.93,1:25:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底想要幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.24,1:25:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了，我要附身在你身上
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.64,1:25:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幹掉那個藏，你覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.34,1:25:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.05,1:25:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊！救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.62,1:25:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你在呼救也不有人來救你的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.23,1:26:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡\N真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.30,1:26:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如跟我合體 一口氣把她解決掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.97,1:26:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.01,1:26:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人是屬於我一個人的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.64,1:26:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就快點動手啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.18,1:26:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別管我喔！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.42,1:26:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有資格命令我
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.96,1:26:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏！藏！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.60,1:27:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.97,1:27:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,札梅帝！這個傢伙也是超能力者
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.99,1:27:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好大的膽子
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.04,1:27:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能死 我要活著保護藏
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.45,1:27:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護藏 藏
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.19,1:28:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.80,1:28:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.77,1:28:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.67,1:28:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是來遲了一步
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.36,1:30:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行，別那麼做
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.86,1:30:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙勒本達，你在阻止什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.70,1:30:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在心中充滿了仇恨想要去報仇啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.93,1:30:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪呀
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.40,1:30:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.77,1:30:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果力量是因為邪惡的念頭而起的話
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.24,1:30:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會導致自身的滅亡
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.94,1:30:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.64,1:30:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣就從一萬五千公里外的紐約飛過來
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.32,1:30:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量應該已經用盡才對
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.45,1:30:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你最好不要逞強
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.69,1:30:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要管我
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.76,1:30:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，不要 你別走
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.73,1:31:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你直意要走的話
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.61,1:31:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就…我們就沒辦法\N跟你一起共同行動了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.24,1:31:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏\N哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.64,1:31:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力防護罩
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.72,1:31:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.09,1:31:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.59,1:32:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有辦法預料我的力量了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.81,1:32:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.55,1:32:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後我到底該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.50,1:33:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅亡！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.67,1:33:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都將會滅亡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.91,1:33:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁華首都，都變成了廢墟
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.22,1:33:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還會變成沒有止境的沙漠
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.90,1:33:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅亡啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.12,1:34:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.86,1:34:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個樣子啊 應該馬上就會復原的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.33,1:34:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切真是多虧了卡福醫生
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.37,1:34:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.90,1:34:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，是你的友情救了他
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.69,1:34:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首都圈已經徹底毀滅了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.93,1:34:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風一下子就停了下來了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.37,1:34:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜下來之後 反而有點陰森森的感覺
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.78,1:35:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，有東西過來
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.30,1:35:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡福醫生 你有沒有聽到什麼聲音呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.23,1:35:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！是地震
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.43,1:36:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是個非常重大的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.73,1:36:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.53,1:36:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，藏 是你的力量阻止了那個的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.54,1:36:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奮力的飛上去吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.86,1:37:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔！跟我預測的一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.97,1:37:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擁有透視未來的能力
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.80,1:37:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的事情之後
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.24,1:37:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就慌慌張張趕來了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.84,1:37:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.94,1:37:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塔歐，因為我接受到露娜的心電感應
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.18,1:37:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.95,1:37:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你看這個
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.45,1:37:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼所有的大樓都朝同樣的方向倒呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.42,1:37:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那邊是地震源
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.59,1:37:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這也是幻魔的搞得鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.79,1:37:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幻魔就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.49,1:37:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有高聳的山脈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.53,1:37:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.20,1:37:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那也是你預測到了？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.31,1:37:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.71,1:37:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我們走
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.15,1:37:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.88,1:37:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是哪裡呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.65,1:38:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.17,1:38:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.51,1:38:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烏
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.72,1:38:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.56,1:38:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是侵入我魔界的人
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.49,1:38:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格殺勿論
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.34,1:38:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻魔在火口裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.81,1:38:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過去
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.51,1:39:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.97,1:39:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了，力量又消失掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.49,1:39:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿議
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.53,1:39:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿議
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.50,1:40:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.65,1:41:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.55,1:41:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說是鹿了 就連救自己的力量都沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.23,1:41:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐，我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.64,1:41:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐，等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.07,1:41:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下啦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.78,1:41:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.20,1:42:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要喝水嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.39,1:42:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.09,1:42:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.97,1:42:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.04,1:42:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是孤零零的一個人
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.38,1:42:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的動物們跟露娜他們
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.65,1:42:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我出生以前就認識的朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.32,1:43:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是在這個叫地球的行星上
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.99,1:43:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育成長的悠久生命
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.32,1:43:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐所說的就是指這件事
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.86,1:43:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你記住這一點
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.96,1:43:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後你所能依靠的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.07,1:43:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就只有愛了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.84,1:43:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.27,1:43:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從幻魔的破壞中保護住地球的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.27,1:43:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是憤怒與憎恨中衍生出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.91,1:43:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是來自對夥伴們的真心關懷
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.28,1:43:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你好久了，藏
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.23,1:43:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四郎
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.63,1:43:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很累了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.90,1:43:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那一臉奇怪的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.67,1:43:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沙堆裡面把你救出來的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.87,1:43:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.97,1:43:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡福醫生說他很遺憾\N你失去了你自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.71,1:43:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡福醫生？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.72,1:44:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.62,1:44:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣，喝一口吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.60,1:44:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會免費奉送喔
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.63,1:44:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼要求？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.70,1:44:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.93,1:44:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.00,1:44:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的那種力量
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.10,1:44:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我幻魔一族繼續效力
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.57,1:44:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,札梅帝
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.28,1:44:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖照我的話去做吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.39,1:44:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做無謂的反抗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.06,1:44:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你就不想活命了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.30,1:44:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算會死 我也不會向你們投降的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.24,1:44:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.49,1:45:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.53,1:45:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子，你還能運用力量
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.37,1:47:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.74,1:47:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.09,1:47:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.56,1:47:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.56,1:47:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞桑西
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.96,1:47:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也接受到露娜的心電感應了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.69,1:48:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.31,1:48:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你流了好多汗 是因為這裡接近火口的緣故
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.68,1:48:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們都沒有流汗耶
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.05,1:48:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.66,1:48:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是這個樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.26,1:48:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人總是胡搞瞎搞的
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.03,1:48:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才看到你戰鬥的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.20,1:48:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不能好好的控制力量
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.23,1:48:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是你還不習慣運用
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.47,1:48:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的力量才會突然出現
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.71,1:48:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然又沒辦法運用
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.98,1:49:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.71,1:49:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，你可以用超能力調整體感溫度吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.93,1:49:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.80,1:49:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已經乾了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.04,1:49:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一課結束
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.33,1:49:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.34,1:49:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻魔一族的卡福
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.04,1:49:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.40,1:50:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我就是這次
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.54,1:50:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球毀滅作戰的最高指揮官嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.49,1:50:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我盡全力來收拾你們吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.83,1:50:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.93,1:51:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜看擁有悠久歷史的智慧型種族
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.77,1:51:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滅亡之城的悲壯之美啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.78,1:51:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的生存意志越強烈的話
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.75,1:51:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會衍生出更悲壯的美感
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.29,1:51:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人類現在就要迎接末日啦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.89,1:51:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們把拼死衹抗的最終美感
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.93,1:51:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底的展現出來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.53,1:51:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很討厭耶
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.90,1:51:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿議，快點躲在我後面
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.47,1:52:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，切換成殘留思念吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.74,1:52:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓放射出去的力量發生持續作用
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.64,1:52:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二課
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.12,1:52:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難不倒我的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.12,1:52:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種絕招你們辦得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.52,1:53:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你們各位徹底地失望的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.02,1:53:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚的遊戲 就請你們到此結束吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.39,1:53:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡就是你們葬生的墓地了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.47,1:53:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成石頭永遠沈睡
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.55,1:53:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始凝固了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.11,1:53:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等凝固到了心臟之後一切就結束了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.95,1:53:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還稍嫌不足
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.06,1:53:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看你們那種悲壯的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.92,1:53:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就承認你們還有一點點美感好了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.80,1:53:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.22,1:54:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.26,1:54:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對不可能是你幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.63,1:54:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰！
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.54,1:54:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了是火焰超能力戰士
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.84,1:54:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐的殘留思念
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.92,1:55:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險喔，差點就變成石頭了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.05,1:55:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了就\N模拜耶
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.46,1:55:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.63,1:55:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是元素遭到轉換了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.70,1:55:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以用超能力透視嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.87,1:56:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.94,1:56:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要維持跳動
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.17,1:56:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即然如此
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.84,1:56:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就試著運用超能力振波按摩
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.23,1:56:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有改變耶
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.30,1:56:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在增強一點力量好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.53,1:57:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.54,1:57:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.57,1:57:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們大家
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.18,1:57:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們添了很多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.08,1:57:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是露娜
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.71,1:57:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我做了對不起你的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.52,1:57:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 其實我對你也太嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.95,1:57:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.89,1:57:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不好
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.42,1:57:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你還年輕
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.29,1:57:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難免會遇到一些不順心的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.36,1:57:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些潛在的超能力也會因此而覺醒
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.37,1:57:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當姐姐的殘留思念毀掉卡福的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.60,1:57:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我強烈的感覺到
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.21,1:57:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛，就是所有力量的來源
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.21,1:57:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三課結束
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.78,1:58:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得不放心
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.15,1:58:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該還記得他的手腕吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.79,1:58:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候\N他的手腕明明就被切斷了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.59,1:58:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻馬上恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.33,1:58:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得那種怪物\N可以簡單消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.73,1:58:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.81,1:58:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他，他又復活了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.15,1:59:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是諾瓦現象
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.92,1:59:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在等這個
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.86,1:59:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你真正的力量了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.56,1:59:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四課已經上完了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.53,1:59:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的決戰就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.04,1:59:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.05,2:01:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊！我們放射的能量
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.98,2:01:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被變換成身體原子反過來攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.25,2:01:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡戰鬥對我們不利
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.62,2:01:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先往上面衝吧
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.69,2:01:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.36,2:01:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原形誘導
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.86,2:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用最後的手段
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.76,2:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.23,2:02:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的身體當做是增幅器
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.23,2:02:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他的能量逆流回去
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.77,2:02:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家現在把力量
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.13,2:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部集合到我的身上來，快
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.97,2:02:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.57,2:02:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏，站在我的正上方
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.48,2:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.31,2:02:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛！
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.25,2:02:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始啦
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.00,2:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位用盡所有的力量
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.99,2:03:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對零度
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.51,2:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.37,2:05:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.71,2:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是貝葛\N不會吧
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.55,2:05:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你們各位
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.95,2:05:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻魔一族已經被消滅掉了
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.06,2:05:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝葛你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,2:05:54.56,2:05:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士也有休息的必要
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.90,2:06:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過這次的休息時間好像長一點
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.57,2:06:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，我不要你這樣
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.04,2:06:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要覺得悲傷
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.37,2:06:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當妳看到絕望的時候
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.84,2:06:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也會因而發生希望
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.15,2:06:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得地球也有一句很美麗的話
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.98,2:06:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當毛毛蟲的未日來臨時
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.19,2:06:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味著蝴蝶即將誕生的事了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.69,2:06:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的生命都會永恆不滅的介入輪迴轉世
Dialogue: 0,2:06:34.40,2:06:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們遭到破壞的故鄉地球
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.50,2:06:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是這個大宇宙中的生命體之一
Dialogue: 0,2:06:43.81,2:06:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一定會復活再次甦醒的
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.92,2:06:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.19,2:07:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士歸來的地方通常都是生命的源頭


